dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.fibex.fibex4ethernet.ethernettopology

Interface IApplicationEndpoint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IApplicationEndpoint
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IApplicationEndpoint: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    An application endpoint is the endpoint on an Ecu in terms of application addressing (e.g. socket). The application endpoint represents e.g. the listen socket in client-server-based communication.
